  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Consecutive living-kidney donor candidates (n=100) will be recruited after being accepted for
      donation according to official guidelines. An assessment of salt sensitivity, 11 beta HSD
      activity, 24 hour blood pressure, urine collection and physical exam will be performed prior
      nephrectomy and 14, 52, 156, 208 days post-nephrectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
